The paper discusses the use of algorithms to create artificial neural networks, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the strengths and weaknesses of human and machine design capacities, which relates to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper proposes a mixed-initiative approach for collaborative online brain building, which involves both machine learning and human input, and could fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and systems and control (cs.SY).
